snippet.title: Quake - Xmas Jam 2020 - Eternal Return - [4K] - [100%]
snippet.description:
Quake Single Player Custom Map
Title : Xmas Jam 2020 - Eternal Return
Author : Benoit "Bal" Stordeur
Release Date : 25.12.2020

New Graphics : Yes
New Music : Yes
Secrets : 3 / 3

This package does not require the main Arcane Dimension mod. All important files are already included in the package!

Based on Arcande Dimension - [Version1.8]

Download: https://www.moddb.com/mods/arcane-dimensions

Description from the Readme:

A map for the 2020 Quake Xmas Jam. Ranger is stuck in a dimensional loop, find a way to escape!

Download : Xmas Jam 2020

http://www.born-robotic.net/stuff/qstuff/xmasjam2020.zip

Played with : AfterQuake Package - [Version 5776 - Win 64] - https://fte.triptohell.info/downloads

I recorded this Custom Single Player Map in UHD - 3840x2160 Pixel.

Recording source is: [Geforce Shadow Play].

Edited with: [Sony Vegas Pro version 17.0].

You have a question or criticism, then write a comment!
